OL,3,CSNP leadership: 'There will be a
OL,4,Ccoronation, not a contest'
OL,6,FSo, after days of "will she, won't
OL,7,Fshe?", we got the answer this
OL,8,Fafternoon.
OL,10,FKate Forbes will not stand to become
OL,11,Fleader of the, and Scotland's next
OL,12,FFirst Minister. There will be a
OL,13,Fcoronation, not a contest.
OL,15,FBarring a late challenger unexpectedly
OL,16,Femerging before nominations close on
OL,17,FMonday John Swinney will be crowned -
OL,18,Fin a political sense - next week,
OL,19,Ftaking over from Humza Yousaf.
