OL,6,FHe had also, as we subsequently
OL,7,Flearned, offered her a big job in
OL,8,Fgovernment if she stood aside and
OL,9,Fbacked him. That's the pragmatic bit.
OL,11,FThe principle lies in the direction Ms
OL,12,FForbes wants to take the party. She
OL,13,Fhas been critical of aspects of the
OL,14,Fnow defunct coalition deal the SNP had
OL,15,Fwith the Scottish Greens.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/11
