OL,6,FHer fears, shared by some within her
OL,7,Fparty, were that by adopting more
OL,8,Fradical policies on climate change the
OL,9,FScottish government was seen as anti-
OL,10,Fgrowth and out of touch with the
OL,11,Fpublic.
OL,13,FNot everyone in the SNP shared this
OL,14,Fview, and the Greens hotly dispute it.
OL,15,FBut it was obvious that, for good or
OL,16,Fill, the administration had been moved
OL,17,Ffurther to the Left as a result of the
OL,18,Ftwo party alliance.
