OL,6,FIn a carefully crafted speech
OL,7,Fannouncing his candidacy this morning,
OL,8,FMr Swinney said this:
OL,10,F"Only the SNP stand where the majority
OL,11,Fof people want their government to be,
OL,12,Fin the moderate centre-left of
OL,13,FScottish politics.
OL,15,F"That is where I stand. And, if
OL,16,Felected by my party and by Parliament,
OL,17,Fmy goals as First Minister will come
OL,18,Fstraight from that moderate centre-
OL,19,Fleft tradition ` the pursuit of
OL,20,Feconomic growth and of social justice.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/11
