OL,6,F"Economic growth, not for its own
OL,7,Fsake, but to support the services and
OL,8,Fsociety we all want to see."
OL,10,FIn her statement released this
OL,11,Fafternoon, Ms Forbes said that the two
OL,12,Fhad "frank and constructive" talks and
OL,13,Fwhat had emerged was they shared "a
OL,14,Fpowerful common purpose for the
OL,15,Fcountry".
