OL,6,FOf the areas they agreed on she added:
OL,7,F"It also includes an understanding
OL,8,Fthat economic growth and tackling
OL,9,Fpoverty must again be key priorities,
OL,10,Fand that a just transition to 'net
OL,11,Fzero' must work with, and not against,
OL,12,Four communities and businesses.
OL,14,F"But more than that, John is clear
OL,15,Fthat he is determined to return the
OL,16,FSNP to governing from the mainstream.
OL,17,FCompetent, candid government earning
OL,18,Fthe trust of the people.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/11
