OL,6,F"That was the vision I offered in the
OL,7,Flast leadership contest, and is
OL,8,Fevidently demanded by the Scottish
OL,9,Fpublic.
OL,11,F"It became obvious listening to Mr
OL,12,FSwinney that by the time he made his
OL,13,Fannouncement, he knew his possible
OL,14,Frival was not going to challenge him,
OL,15,Fand that they had agreed common ground
OL,16,Fbetween them. And so it turned out.
OL,17,FThe reaction of the opposition to the
OL,18,Flikely new combination at the top of
OL,19,Fthe Scottish government was not
OL,20,Fexactly subtle, not uncommon in
OL,21,Fpartisan exchanges.
