OL,6,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,7,FPolitics? Every week Tom, Robert and
OL,8,FAnushka dig into the biggest issues
OL,9,Fdominating the political agenda...
OL,11,FScottish Conservative leader Douglas
OL,12,FRoss said: "Kate Forbes has caved into
OL,13,FSNP demands for a stitch-up to install
OL,14,FJohn Swinney as leader and spare the
OL,15,Fparty the bloodbath of another
OL,16,Fleadership contest.
OL,18,F"But this shady backroom deal won't
OL,19,Fcover-up the bitter splits that exist
OL,20,Fwithin the SNP ` it just applies a
OL,21,Fsticking plaster to a gaping wound.
