OL,6,F"We'll be hearing a lot of this kind
OL,7,Fof thing in the run up to the UK
OL,8,Felection and beyond. Observers think
OL,9,Fthe polls suggest their fortunes have
OL,10,Fdipped so far that they may face a
OL,11,Fhuge challenge for the UK elections.
OL,13,FBut the next Holyrood ballot will be
OL,14,Fin 2026, giving more time to reset and
OL,15,Frecalibrate.
OL,17,FThe question is whether that is a
OL,18,Fcredible line of attack, whether it
OL,19,Fchimes with what the public think, and
OL,20,Fwhat it is sustainable?
