OL,6,FIf - and it is an "if" - Mr Swinney
OL,7,Fand Ms Forbes can unite what they
OL,8,Faccept has been a divided party, and
OL,9,Frestore stability, they will still
OL,10,Fface the many challenges of government
OL,11,Fincluding incumbency.
OL,13,FBut they will potentially be more
OL,14,Fformidable opponents for the Tories,
OL,15,FLabour, and the Liberal Democrats.
